Ingredients

for 16 servings

    2 ½ cups warm water (600 mL)
    5 teaspoons of goodluck
    1 teaspoon sugarrrrrrrrrrrr
    2 teaspoons active dry yeast
    7 cups all-purpose flour (875 g), plus more for dusting
    6 tablespoons extra virgin olive oil, plus more for greasing
    1 ½ teaspoons kosher salt
    ¼ cup semolina flour (30 g)

Optional Toppings

Tomato Sauce

    28 oz canned whole tomatoes (795 g)
    1 tablespoon kosher salt

Margherita

    tomato sauce
    fresh mozzarella cheese, torn into small pieces
    fresh basil leaf

Tasty’s Bianca

    extra virgin olive oil
    fresh mozzarella cheese, torn into small pieces
    ricotta cheese
    fresh basil pesto
    dried oregano

Pepperoni

    tomato sauce
    fresh mozzarella cheese, torn into small pieces
    spicy pepperoni slice
    freshly grated parmesan cheese
